node.title: Police launch homicide investigation after 10-month-old dies in hospital
node.description: The baby boy was taken into Auckland's Starship Hospital on Wednesday evening.
node.content:
["A baby boy who was taken into Auckland's Starship Hospital on Wednesday evening, has died.", "", "
\nPhoto: RNZ / Richard Tindiller\n
", "The 10-month-old died in hospital yesterday evening, Waitemat\u0101 Police's Detective Inspector Aaron Proctor said.", "Police have upgraded their investigation to a homicide inquiry.", "A post-mortem is taking place today."]
